<div class="tt"><h1>美女解读红酒减肥偏方<b>乐购 / 2011-09-17</b></h1><span></span></div>
<div class="ct"><div class="bgw p1-0">
 <div id="art_contain"> 
          <p>&nbsp;<span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; "><br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: 'andale mono', times; "><span style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: large; "><strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; "><img src="http://www.365wine.com/media/enterprise/4846717623981298148.jpg" alt="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; vertical-align: top; " /><br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
</strong></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 红酒减肥偏方解读： 红酒能减肥的传闻在网络已经风行了很久。该方法认为睡前喝一杯红酒吃奶酪，能促进新陈代谢，燃烧腰部和臀部的脂肪。只要3餐正常吃，在睡前30分内，吃1～2片起司或50g乳酪，再喝1杯50～100c.c.的红酒，3周可瘦7公斤。 认为红酒能减肥的理由如下：<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<strong style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-weight: bold; ">A.提高新陈代谢：红酒中所含的维他命C、E及胡萝卜素其抗氧化力，能提高原本随着年龄而降低的新陈代谢。<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
B.避免暴食暴饮：当然，血中酒精浓度也会缓慢升高，对解除压力也有效果，因此也能抑制压力性的暴食暴饮。<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
C.减少体内水肿：红酒含有丰富铁质，加上酒精本身具有活血暖身的作用，因此可以改善贫血，暖和腰肾，有效减少身体内水分的堆积。浮肿体质者尤其适合这种既美肤又纤体的红酒瘦身法。<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
</strong>&nbsp;网友体验&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
经过调查发现，绝大多数的mm试验红酒减肥法均以失败告终。看来，想依赖红酒就能瘦个十几斤的梦想是不现实的：&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
已经试过了，对我没起效果。&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
这东西我原来老吃,可是吃得发胖啊。&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
喝完了一瓶红酒加两袋奶酪　无效放弃&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
基本米效果，去年试过，太恶心了。不过每天喝点红酒倒不错&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
真相：红酒对减肥的作用非常之小，喝太多会让你长胖。&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
首先我们要了解一下人为什么会长胖除了疾病性原因，大多数人的肥胖都是因为吃入的热量大于消耗的热量，多余的热量慢慢地在身体里累积成了脂肪。所以，要想减肥应该要同时控制吃入的热量，同时还要增加消耗的热量。&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
想喝红酒减肥的MM如果三餐照旧，又吃了红酒奶酪，那么摄入的热量不仅没有减少，反而增多了;其次，即便是红酒有促进新陈代谢的作用，但是如果不配合运动，这点作用是非常微小的，无法抵消红酒带来的多余热量，更谈不上减肥啦。&nbsp;<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
<br style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; " />
纯正的红酒所含的热量比较低，少量饮用和肥胖并没有直接关系。但是现在市场上卖的一些红酒不是真正的葡萄酒，而是采用多种原料调配、勾兑成的，这些原料中又通常含有糖分和添加剂成分，热量自然会比较高，也就容易发胖。所以要提醒大家，购买时一定要选正规厂家生产的葡萄酒。好的葡萄酒完全由葡萄发酵而成，味道甘酸、微甜，不含任何添加剂。那种喝起来比较甜的红酒，都加入了很多糖，这样一杯250毫升红酒，与一碗白饭的热量差不多，约240卡路里。</span></p>                           
